Artist/Studio
-------------------
 - Plan (Free, Pro)

Subscription
__________________
- user_id
- studio_id
- artist_id
- plan
- start_date
- status (active, closed, deactivated)
- payment_frequency

payments/statements/
_____________________
- subscription_id
- amount
- paid_by
- datetime
- payment_method ()
- status (paid, unpaid, overdue)
- response
- (token or card stored in)


Workflow
---------
- signup
- choose account type
- collect payment method
- charge first month (schedule job to process payments monthly or yearly)
- Email customer on successful charge/failure and when payment is close to happening. 
